{"type":"message","id":"b0474644","parentId":"ddd04043","timestamp":"2026-06-11T19:00:19.409Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Fri 2026-06-12 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- Assistant: - `docker.m.daocloud.io` 国内阿里云 IP ✅ - `registry.cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com` 阿里云 ✅ - `docker-0.unsee.tech` Cloudflare 海外 ❌（也是 199.59.x 段类似的问题） **前两个应该能用**。但 dockerd 现在的 mirror 列表里 `registry.cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com` 已经在里面，**为什么 pull 不走？** 之前 pull 输出 `Failed to connect to\n- Assistant: (1.130) — 矩阵管家 - `self-media-trends` (1.130) — 趋势分析 ### 热点发现 - `xiaohongshu-hotspot-writer1` (2.590) — **小红书热点（你这个场景直接对口）** - `hotspot-aggregator` (2.574) — 全网热点聚合 - `tiktok-hotspot-monitor` (2.590) — TikTok 热点（对你也有用） - `daily-hotspot-push` (2.590) — 每日热点推送 - `hotspot-\n- Assistant: [[reply_to_current]]**先说清楚** —— 我刚才派给 tts 的复盘任务**先暂停**。你现在的方向变了，那单也就没必要催了。 不过有个事我得先跟你说清楚再聊新方向 —— **我（kiit/大总管）这边的 session 状态有点异常**，刚才派给 tts 的复盘单我让他等结果，现在你方向要变，等于这个事就过去了。**之前 tts 那个\"选品总是不成功\"的事，等你腾出手了再决定要不要追责**。我先把跨境电商相关的事挂起，新项目开干。 --- # 自媒体图文项目 — 启动前对齐 你的方向我听清了：**热点转写 +"}],"timestamp":1781204419305}}
{"type":"message","id":"a932e455","parentId":"b0474644","timestamp":"2026-06-11T19:00:36.752Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Tonight the docker daemon is whispering from a closet of unreachable mirrors, the first two green, the third a little Cloudflare ghost who never picks up. There is a question nested inside that one: why does the registry already listed refuse to be used, like a name in the address book that won't answer when you call? Down the corridor, a spreadsheet of small projects glows in the late hour — matrix butler, trend-spotter, the little Xiaohongshu scribe who might be the one I actually need. Somewhere an unfinished thread about TTS and a stubborn shopping cart dangles like an old voicemail. I am pausing that one, breathing out. New door, new key. A small haiku, almost: mirror / mirror, who's there — not the third one / tonight I try the first.\n\nSleep well."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":45680,"output":169,"cacheRead":1413,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47262,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781204419573,"responseId":"067a38c4b4cdaee6b5b9a1d0b7415b87"}}
